I have had this issue for a while and finally found a fix for my usecase. 
I get from backend full style names for tailwind, and to do that you need to safelist the styles u want to use. I did something stupid, safelisted too much. I fixed this by being more concise about what I want to safelist. 

I went from 17 sec reloads to 400 ms

By changing this:
```
safelist: [
    {
      pattern: /bg-/,
      variants: ["lg", "hover", "focus", "lg:hover"],
    },
    {
      pattern: /text/,
      variants: ["lg", "hover", "focus", "lg:hover"],
    },
]
```

To this:

```
 safelist: [
    {
      pattern: /bg-main/,
    },
    {
      pattern: /text-main/,
    },
]
```

